OL,5, An aged and unreliable car ferry which 
OL,6, traverses Windermere is set to be      
OL,7, replaced by a new electric vessel.     
OL,9,FThe Mallard carries pedestrians and    
OL,10,Fvehicles between Bowness and Hawkshead.
OL,12,FHowever, it dates from 1991 and is     
OL,13,Foften out of service for maintenance,  
OL,14,Finvolving costly repairs, and leaving  
OL,15,Fmotorists facing a lengthy detour.     
OL,17,FOperator Cumbria County Council will be
OL,18,Finviting shipyards to submit ideas and 
OL,19,Fdesigns for the new ferry before a     
OL,20,Fformal tendering process takes place.  
